  <h2>Key Publications</h2>
  <p>
    The HAIF framework and its application are documented in the following key references:
  </p>
  <ul>
    <li>
      Aarons, G. A., Hurlburt, M. &amp; Horwitz, S. M. (2011). Advancing a
      conceptual model of evidence-based practice implementation in public
      service sectors. <em>Administration and Policy in Mental Health</em>,
      38(1), 4-23. [EPIS model]
    </li>
    <li>
      Lee, A., Chan, S. K. &amp; Fan, L. T. (2015). Stimulation of the wrist
      acupuncture point PC6 for preventing postoperative nausea and vomiting.
      <em>Cochrane Database of Systematic Reviews</em>, (11), CD003281. [Primary evidence source]
    </li>
    <li>
      Cheong, K. B. et al. (2013). The effectiveness of acupuncture in prevention
      and treatment of postoperative nausea and vomiting. <em>PLoS ONE</em>, 8(12),
      e82474. [Systematic review and meta-analysis]
    </li>
  </ul>
